      "description": "2021 Honda Accord in good condition. The interior shows normal wear from regular use, including light scuffs on trim surfaces and some fading on high-contact areas. The upholstery is intact with no major damage. The exterior has a few small scratches and minor paint blemishes but no significant dents or structural issues. Mechanically sound with no known issues.",
