    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Ready for your next adventure? This well-maintained vehicle is in genuinely good condition \u2014 and it shows in every detail! The exterior presents nicely with only minor signs of everyday use, and the interior is clean and comfortable. Mechanically sound and dependable, this car has been cared for and is ready to hit the road. A fantastic value for a quality ride \u2014 come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 32000.0,
